title: OKdo ROCK 5 AIO Edge Media Board with 3 TOPs NPU and Pre-integrated AI Stack
description: The OKdo ROCK 5 AIO Edge AI Media Board, belonging to the ROCK Series, features a 3 TOPS NPU. It incorporates an AI stack designed for compatibility with GStreamer and OpenCV, suitable for custom computer vision projects.
